---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="TaskAI â€” Stop juggling AI tools. Start assigning work.">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Glow orbs -->
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-blue/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-brand-teal/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-1/3 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-orange/15 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center py-24">
      <img src="/images/logo-light.png" alt="TaskAI" class="mx-auto h-20 md:h-28 mb-10" />
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-brand-blue to-brand-teal bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight">
        Stop juggling AI tools.<br />Start assigning work.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        TaskAI is the first workspace where you manage tasks, chat with AI, and collaborate with your team â€” all in one place. Think of it as a project manager that actually does the work.
      </p>

      <!-- Email form -->
      <form id="hero-form" action="#" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <input type="hidden" name="source" value="taskai-landing" />
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          required
          placeholder="you@example.com"
          class="flex-1 px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white/10 border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue/60 transition"
        />
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="px-8 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-blue to-brand-teal font-semibold text-white hover:opacity-90 transition shadow-lg shadow-brand-blue/25"
        >
          Get Early Access
        </button>
      </form>
      <p id="hero-thanks" class="hidden mt-4 text-brand-teal font-medium">ðŸŽ‰ You're on the list! We'll be in touch soon.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM -->
  <section class="relative py-24 px-6">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-brand-coral/5 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16">Sound familiar?</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md">
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white mb-3 italic">"I have 12 ChatGPT tabs open and none of them remember what I said yesterday."</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">You're copying context between tools, repeating yourself to AI, and losing track of what was decided where.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md">
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white mb-3 italic">"My AI can write a blog post, but I still have to manage every step myself."</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">AI is powerful in isolation â€” but without task management, you're still the bottleneck organizing all the pieces.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md">
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white mb-3 italic">"Half my team uses AI. The other half doesn't. Nothing connects."</p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Your workflow is split between humans and AI tools with no shared workspace. Handoffs are messy, context gets lost.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <section class="relative py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">One workspace. AI and humans. Real work getting done.</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">TaskAI brings your tasks, your team, and your AI agents into one place â€” so you can focus on the work that matters.</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { icon: 'ðŸ“‹', title: 'Task boards that actually work', desc: 'Kanban boards, priorities, deadlines, subtasks. Assign work to an AI agent or a team member â€” same board, same workflow.' },
          { icon: 'ðŸ’¬', title: 'Chat that\'s connected to your work', desc: 'Every task has a conversation. Ask your AI agent a question, give feedback, iterate â€” all in context. No more "let me find that thread."' },
          { icon: 'ðŸ§ ', title: 'AI that remembers', desc: 'Your agents build knowledge over time. They remember your preferences, past decisions, and project context â€” so you\'re not starting from scratch every conversation.' },
          { icon: 'ðŸ‘¥', title: 'Human + AI, side by side', desc: 'Assign a research task to AI. Hand the results to your copywriter. They collaborate in the same workspace. No separate tools, no lost context.' },
          { icon: 'ðŸ“±', title: 'Works where you do', desc: 'Web app, iPhone, Android. Create tasks by voice, check in on progress during your commute, approve AI work from your phone.' },
          { icon: 'ðŸ”', title: 'Your data stays yours', desc: 'AI runs on your infrastructure with your API keys. Nothing passes through servers you don\'t control. Full privacy, full ownership.' },
        ].map(({ icon, title, desc }) => (
          <div class="group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-brand-blue/30 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">{icon}</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="relative py-24 px-6">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-brand-blue/5 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16">Three steps to a smarter workflow</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {[
          { step: '1', title: 'Create a task', desc: 'Describe what you need â€” "Write a proposal for the Henderson account" or "Research competitors in the Austin market." Quick text, voice note, or detailed brief.' },
          { step: '2', title: 'Assign it', desc: 'Route it to an AI agent for instant work, a team member for the human touch, or both. TaskAI doesn\'t care who does the work â€” it cares that it gets done.' },
          { step: '3', title: 'Review and ship', desc: 'AI delivers drafts, research, code, or analysis. You review, give feedback in the task chat, and iterate until it\'s right. Then move on to what\'s next.' },
        ].map(({ step, title, desc }) => (
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-teal flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold shadow-lg shadow-brand-blue/25">
              {step}
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EARLY ACCESS CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to put AI to work?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Join the waitlist for early access. We're onboarding teams now â€” first come, first served.</p>

        <form id="cta-form" action="#" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto">
          <input type="hidden" name="source" value="taskai-landing" />
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            required
            placeholder="you@example.com"
            class="flex-1 px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white/10 border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-blue/60 transition"
          />
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="px-8 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-orange to-brand-coral font-semibold text-white hover:opacity-90 transition shadow-lg shadow-brand-coral/25"
          >
            Join the Waitlist
          </button>
        </form>
        <p id="cta-thanks" class="hidden mt-4 text-brand-teal font-medium">ðŸŽ‰ You're on the list! We'll be in touch soon.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500 text-sm">Free to start. No credit card required.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="border-t border-white/10 py-10 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-gray-500 text-sm">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} BUILD3R LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
      <a href="https://build3r.io" class="hover:text-white transition">BUILD3R.io</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('#hero-form, #cta-form').forEach(form => {
      form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        const thanks = form.parentElement?.querySelector('[id$="-thanks"]') || form.nextElementSibling;
        form.classList.add('hidden');
        if (thanks) thanks.classList.remove('hidden');
      });
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
